      "Code": "// Graph 1 - Report Configuration\n\n// Sheet names (one per data package from ConMan)\n[\"Connector Actions\", \"Metrics\"];\n\n\"Insert_Connectors_Report.xlsx\";\n // Saves to Desktop if just filename;\n\n\"Blue\";\n // Theme: Blue / Green / Red / Purple / Orange / Teal / custom hex;",
